            "summary": "Animation Designs: Arctic Anecdotes - I created a loose idea for a kids show which followed an indigenous grandmother travelling through the Arctic, solving&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Animation Designs:</span></h2>\n<p>Arctic Anecdotes - I created a loose idea for a kids show which followed an indigenous grandmother travelling through the Arctic, solving any mysteries or conflict she may come across. I was then tasked with designing the main character, props, creatures as well as a layout:</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLineup.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLineup-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Lineup\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Lineup</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticVehicle.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticVehicle-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Vehicle\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Vehicle</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticProp.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticProp-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Prop\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Prop</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticPropPose.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticPropPose-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Prop Posing\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Prop Posing</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticPoses.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticPoses-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Character Posing\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Character Posing</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLayoutComp.png\" data-size=\"4800x2700\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLayoutComp-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Layout Composition\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Layout Composition</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLayout.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_ArcticLayout-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Arctic Anecdotes Layout Painting\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a>\n<figcaption>Arctic Anecdotes Layout Painting</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Extra Designs:</span></h2>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_DnDLineup.png\" data-size=\"4200x2550\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_DnDLineup-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"DnD Character Lineup\" width=\"768\" height=\"466\"></a>\n<figcaption>DnD Character Lineup</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_DnDPosing.png\" data-size=\"4200x2550\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_DnDPosing-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"DnD Character Posing\" width=\"768\" height=\"466\"></a>\n<figcaption>DnD Character Posing</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_Barbershop.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_Barbershop-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Barbershop Layout\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_Street.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/ILLUSTRATION_Street-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Street Layout\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/Eric_PNGtuber_v1.png\" data-size=\"3200x1800\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/Eric_PNGtuber_v1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Pizza Character Posing\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Personal Work:</span></h2>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/DnDCom.png\" data-size=\"3690x2160\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/DnDCom-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"DnD Commission\" width=\"768\" height=\"450\"></a>\n<figcaption>DnD Commission</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/Shadow-Acne-V3.png\" data-size=\"2118x2715\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/Shadow-Acne-V3-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"T-Shirt Design\" width=\"768\" height=\"984\"></a>\n<figcaption>T-Shirt Design</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/BigTop_fanart_1.png\" data-size=\"2400x3000\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/BigTop_fanart_1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Bigtop Burger Fanart\" width=\"768\" height=\"960\"></a>\n<figcaption>Bigtop Burger Fanart</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/furry-profile.png\" data-size=\"1526x1053\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/furry-profile-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Cat Character Card\" width=\"768\" height=\"530\"></a>\n<figcaption>Cat Character Card</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/RoeBow2.png\" data-size=\"1200x945\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/RoeBow2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"RoeBow Character Card\" width=\"768\" height=\"605\"></a>\n<figcaption>RoeBow Character Card</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/RoeBow_Sketch_Sans.png\" data-size=\"1575x1032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rocketbow.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/5/gallery/RoeBow_Sketch_Sans-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Sans Fanart\" width=\"768\" height=\"503\"></a>\n<figcaption>Sans Fanart</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>",
